<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[شَجَّ]</span>: شَجُّ الرأسِ: شَقُّه.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[ح]</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[شَحَّ]</span>: الشُّحُّ: البخل،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَمَنْ يُوقَ شُحَّ نَفْسِهِ فَأُولائِكَ هُمُ الْمُفْلِحُونَ* <span class="c2">«٣»</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
